The pilgrim must also be mindful of the conduct during Hajj. The Quran prohibits *rafath* (obscenity), *fusuq* (sin), and *jidal* (quarrelling) (<Citation source="Quran" book="2" number="197" href="https://quran.com/2/197" />). This includes avoiding arguments, even if one is in the right, and controlling one’s temper. It is a time for patience, humility, and reflection.

